(693, 'cs95buss', 'chasse', 'COLD STEEL', 'Cold Steel bushman', 'Cold Steel Bushman. 12 1/4" overall. 7" blade. SK-5 high carbon steel construction. The handle is a hollow cylinder perfect for carrying small objects. Versatile design, attaches easily to a shaft so it can be used in an emergency as a hatchet, machete, or spear. Cordura belt sheath.', 'cs95buss.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 29, 'out of stock'),
