(709, '100400c', 'flashlight', 'Bushnell', 'Bushnell HD Torch', 'Edge to edge, no flashlight in the world today delivers a comparable level of radiant intensity and consistency of brightness.\r\n\r\nEvenly distributed square beam light pattern\r\nPowerful 165-lumen output \r\n1.5-hour continuous run time\r\nRugged, waterproof, aircraft-grade aluminum housing with hard-anodized finish that won’t scratch or mar\r\nFind-Me feature and battery-life indicator\r\nIncludes two 3-volt lithium batteries', '100400c.png', 'Aircraft grade aluminium. Waterproof.', NULL, NULL, 'VJh8W6iaqQ8', 79, NULL),
